Read This!

How to Install:

Open the ".zip" file and drag the cstrike folder into your:
 " c:/programfiles/steam/steamapps/counterstrike-source/" or
 " c:/programfiles/valve/steam/steamapps/counterstrike-source/"

Map made by:

Deafult. (RapID css)
Textures made by:

Horrorfilms, Valve and Deafult.

Overview included in bsp :D

Description:

A big map witch is perfect for any weapon.
Very optimized with both areaportals and hint/skip brushes.
Of course nodraw in every non-visible area of the map.

A kind of train/mall map within a big city.
It contains a Long and easy cover underground with many ways out.
All the sodamachines works and the phone actually rings after a while.

If you like the map, please leave a comment on my map site on FPSB.
If you dont like it, please inform me of what I could do better. :D
If you want me to make more maps like this, please leave a comment and say what kinda map you want me to make :P

Hope U like it :D
